- Future Enhancements
- More Drawing Tools: Add additional drawing tools like a brush, fill tool, line tool, etc.
- Onion Skinning: Implement onion skinning to visualize previous frames.
- Color Picker: Allow users to select any color using a color picker.
- Saving and Loading: Enable users to save and load their animations.
- Sound: Add the ability to include soundtracks for animations.
- Advanced UI: Improve the user interface with more features and a more polished look.
